steps.name: I am on the Home Page "http://www.carsguide.com.au" of Car Guide website
move to "buy + sell"
click on "Search Cars" link
select carbrand as "BMW" from AnyMake dropdown
select carmodel as "1 Series" from SelectModel dropdown
select location as "ACT - All" from SelectLocation dropdown
select price as "$10,000" from price dropdown
click on Find_My_Next_Car button
I should see list of searched cars from "BMW"
the page title should be "Bmw 1 Series Under 10000 for Sale ACT | carsguide"
